  "texts": [
    "This raises the second set of research questions with regard to the consolidation of these annotation schemes.",
    "Prior work [53] annotated a dataset multiple times with different schemes and analysed the multi-variate frequency distributions of the classes.",
    "They found that the investigated schemes are complementary and should be combined.",
    "However, anno-tating datasets multiple times is costly and time-consuming.",
    "To support the consolidation of different annotation schemes across domains, we examine the following RQs:#RQ5 Can a model trained with multiple datasets recognise the semantic relatedness of classes from different annotation schemes?"
  ],
